RDF Utils
=========

Simple utility scripts processing RDF data, to remove the need for copying
code across multiple projects. This is not meant for real use.

Dependencies
------------

* Python: https://www.python.org/
* RDFLib: https://github.com/RDFLib/rdflib

Development setup
-----------------

The repository contains a Visual Studio Code Dev Containers definition,
that should contain everything necessary for developing the application.

Issues
------

Please feel free to report any issues on the GitHub issue tracker.

